ygData.messageBody:
There is a file in the eq directory that contains spell info. I was looking
through it a while back and there was a spell called aqua lung. My guess is
that this is what we are looking for. We might want to start asking "what
about the aqua lung" to all the gnome npc's. I am at work, so I can not
verify that it was called aqua lung, but I am 95% sure thats what it was
called. Can someone that knows how to use a hex editor verify this for me?
Otherwise I have to wait until I get home from work.
